						<li><c>particular</c></li>
					</ul>
				</p>

				<p>
					<em>Tip: Double-click a term above to quickly highlight it for copying.</em>
				</p>

				<p>
					<ul marker="square">
						<li>
							<p>
								A family of solutions is the collection of all <fillin width="7" mode="string" answer="particular" /> solutions.
							</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<p>
								A <fillin width="7" mode="string" answer="general" /> solution is a template for each <fillin width="7" mode="string" answer="particular" /> solution.
							</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<p>
								A <fillin width="7" mode="string" answer="general" /> solution can generate a family of solutions.
							</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<p>
								A <fillin width="7" mode="string" answer="general" /> solution contains one or more arbitrary constants.
							</p>
						</li>
